Package: MHDetect
Type: Package
Title: Algorithm for Detecting and Classifying Indels as MMEJ-Dependent
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Daria", 
           family = "Kostka", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "daria.kostka@polsl.pl")
Description: MHDetect is an algorithm for detecting and classifying indels 
    (deletions, insertions, and MNVs) as microhomology-mediated end joining 
    (MMEJ)-dependent.
